    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.98 * tmp + 0.55)) / 0.47)
    v2 = 0.96
    v1 = wp.cos(0.11)
    v1 = wp.exp((tmp / wp.abs(v0 + 0.89)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.87)))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.exp(tmp + 0.70) - 0.04))
